---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Why Attend"
  description="Six reasons to attend EoES 2027 — hands-on workshops, expert sessions, community, free conference day in Norwich."
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="bg-year" aria-hidden="true">?</div>
  <span class="spark" style="top: 22%; left: 7%;"></span>
  <span class="spark sm" style="top: 70%; right: 12%;"></span>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow"><div class="chip chip--pink"><span class="dot"></span><span>Why Attend · 2027</span></div></div>
    <h1 class="display-1 hero-title" style="max-width: 16ch;">Six reasons<br><span class="display-italic">not to miss it.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Whether you're brand new to Power Platform or have years of experience, EoES 2027 has something genuinely valuable for you. Here's why we think you should be there.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="issue-mark"><b>Vol — 02</b> &nbsp;·&nbsp; Why Attend</div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-3">
      <article class="card"><span class="card-num">01</span>
        <div class="card-icon yellow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9.66 17h4.67M12 3v1m6.36 1.64l-.7.7M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.34-5.66l-.7-.7m2.82 9.9a5 5 0 117.07 0l-.55.55A3.37 3.37 0 0014 18.47V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.53c0-.9-.36-1.75-1-2.39l-.54-.54z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Learn from real practitioners</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Every session is delivered by someone who works with Power Platform day-to-day in real organisations. No marketing fluff — just practical knowledge you can apply on Monday morning.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card"><span class="card-num">02</span>
        <div class="card-icon pink"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.36-1.86M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.66-.13-1.28-.36-1.86M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.36-1.86m0 0a5 5 0 019.28 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 116 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Build your network</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Connect with hundreds of Power Platform professionals from across the East of England and beyond. The people who answer your questions, share opportunities and become long-term collaborators.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card"><span class="card-num">03</span>
        <div class="card-icon cyan"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Hands-on workshops</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Friday is a full day of immersive, instructor-led workshops. You won't just watch — you'll build something real. Choose the session that fits your level and walk away with working code.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card"><span class="card-num">04</span>
        <div class="card-icon purple"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 8c-1.66 0-3 .9-3 2s1.34 2 3 2 3 .9 3 2-1.34 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.4 2.6 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.4-2.6-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Free conference day</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Saturday is completely free. No catch, no paywall. EoES is a community event run by volunteers — we believe access to quality learning shouldn't cost you anything.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card"><span class="card-num">05</span>
        <div class="card-icon yellow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17.66 16.66L13.41 20.9a2 2 0 01-2.83 0l-4.24-4.24a8 8 0 1111.31 0zM15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Right here in the East</h3>
        <p class="card-body">World-class Power Platform content without the London price tag or travel cost. Central Norwich, easily reached by rail from across Norfolk, Suffolk, Cambridgeshire and beyond.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card"><span class="card-num">06</span>
        <div class="card-icon pink"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4.32 6.32a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.36L12 20.36l7.68-7.68a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.36-6.36L12 7.64l-1.32-1.32a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.36 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">A welcoming community</h3>
        <p class="card-body">EoES grows from the NPPUG community — known for being friendly, inclusive and supportive. You won't feel like an outsider. Everyone's here to learn and share.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 920px;">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="eyebrow">— Who should come —</div>
      <h2 class="display-3">Useful at <span class="display-italic">every level.</span></h2>
      <p class="sub">EoES is designed to be valuable whether you're brand new or a seasoned practitioner. Here's how different attendees benefit.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stack-4">
      <details class="persona">
        <summary>I'm new to Power Platform</summary>
        <div class="content">
          <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">EoES is one of the best places to start. You'll find introductory sessions pitched at beginners, a workshop day where you build something guided step-by-step, and a community of experienced practitioners happy to answer questions and point you in the right direction.</p>
          <p>You'll leave with a clearer picture of what Power Platform can do, where to focus your learning, and contacts who can help you along the way.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="persona">
        <summary>I'm an experienced Power Platform professional</summary>
        <div class="content">
          <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">There are advanced sessions, deep-dives and workshops designed for people who already know their way around the platform. You'll encounter techniques you haven't seen before, and be challenged to go further.</p>
          <p>Beyond the content, you'll meet peers at your level who face the same challenges — and the connections made here have a way of turning into collaborations, job opportunities and friendships.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="persona">
        <summary>I'm a business analyst, IT manager or decision-maker</summary>
        <div class="content">
          <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">EoES gives you a clear, unbiased view of what Power Platform can realistically deliver for your organisation — shown through real case studies from people who've shipped it, not sales pitches from vendors.</p>
          <p>You'll see the platform in action, ask candid questions, and meet the kind of consultants and developers who could help you if you decided to move forward.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="persona">
        <summary>I'm a student or career-changer</summary>
        <div class="content">
          <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">The Power Platform ecosystem is one of the fastest-growing areas in tech, and EoES is a brilliant way to fast-track your understanding of what the market actually needs and how organisations are using these tools right now.</p>
          <p>Attending puts you in a room with hiring managers, consultants and developers who actively look for motivated newcomers. Bring your questions — and your business cards.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-2" style="align-items: start; gap: 56px;">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 22px;">— What you'll take away —</div>
        <h2 class="display-3" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">More than just<br><span class="display-italic">a lanyard.</span></h2>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;">
          <li><strong style="color: var(--ink-0); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Practical skills</strong><br><span class="muted">Techniques and patterns you can implement immediately — whether from a workshop or a conference session.</span></li>
          <li><strong style="color: var(--ink-0); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">New connections</strong><br><span class="muted">A network of peers, mentors and potential collaborators you simply don't find at online events.</span></li>
          <li><strong style="color: var(--ink-0); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Industry perspective</strong><br><span class="muted">A clearer view of where Power Platform is heading and how others are solving problems similar to yours.</span></li>
          <li><strong style="color: var(--ink-0); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Confidence</strong><br><span class="muted">Seeing others at your level sharing their work is one of the most motivating things you can experience.</span></li>
          <li><strong style="color: var(--ink-0); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Resources</strong><br><span class="muted">Slides, repos and follow-up content from every session — made available to attendees after the event.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="stack-5">
        <article class="card" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--yellow); padding-left: 28px;">
          <div class="chip chip--yellow" style="font-size: 10px;"><span class="dot"></span>Day 01 · Fri 30 Apr 2027</div>
          <h3 class="card-title" style="margin-top: 16px;">Workshop Day</h3>
          <p class="card-body" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Hands-on learning at a Norwich venue (announced soon).</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; color: var(--ink-3); font-size: 14px;">
            <li>+ Full-day, instructor-led workshops</li>
            <li>+ Multiple tracks across experience levels</li>
            <li>+ Paid ticket · limited places</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--pink); padding-left: 28px;">
          <div class="chip chip--pink" style="font-size: 10px;"><span class="dot"></span>Day 02 · Sat 1 May 2027</div>
          <h3 class="card-title" style="margin-top: 16px;">Conference Day</h3>
          <p class="card-body" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Full conference programme at a Norwich venue (announced soon).</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; color: var(--ink-3); font-size: 14px;">
            <li>+ Parallel tracks · keynote · expo hall</li>
            <li>+ Networking lunch included</li>
            <li>+ Completely free to attend</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container center">
    <div class="eyebrow eyebrow--center" style="margin-bottom: 22px;">— Ready to join us —</div>
    <h2 class="display-2" style="max-width: 22ch; margin: 0 auto 22px;">Save the date.<br><span class="display-italic">Follow for updates.</span></h2>
    <p class="lead muted" style="max-width: 56ch; margin: 0 auto 36px;">Workshop tickets and the full programme drop on LinkedIn first. Conference day will always be free.</p>
    <div class="row" style="justify-content: center; gap: 12px;">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/eoes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Follow on LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="/schedule" class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg">View schedule</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
